距離と内積の関係¶

$\langle x,y\rangle$$x,y$($R^m$ ) 2$x,y$$d(x,y)$

$$d(x,y)^2 = \langle x-y, x-y\rangle = \langle x,x\rangle -2\langle x,y\rangle+\langle y,y\rangle$$

$n$$m$$x_1, x_2, \cdots, x_n$ $$X = ix_in \times m$$ $$XX^T = (i,j)\langle x_i, x_j\rangle $$

($X^T$$X$)

$$N_r = i\langle x_i, x_i\rangle$$

$$N_c = i\langle x_i, x_i\rangle $$$$D^2 = (i,j)d(x_i, x_j)^2$$

$$ D^2 = N_r -2XX^T +N_c $$ ($(i,j)$$=d(x_i, x_j)$, $=\langle x_i,x_i\rangle -2\langle x_i,x_j\rangle+\langle x_j,x_j\rangle$)

$A$$A$$0$$diag(A)$

$$N_r = diag(XX^T)\mathbb{1}_n \mathbb{1}_n^{T}$$ $$N_c = \mathbb{1}_n \mathbb{1}_n^{T} diag(XX^T)$$

Kullback-Leibler divergence Kullback-Leibier divergence

$\frac{\partial D(p\| q)}{\partial Y_{i}} = 4\sum_{j}(p_{ij}-q_{ij})(1+\|Y_{i}-Y_{j}\|^2)^{-1}(Y_{i}-Y_{j})$


$d_{ij}=\|Y_{i}-Y_{j}\|^2$$Y_{i}$$d_{i\cdot}$ \begin{eqnarray*} \frac{\partial D(p\| q)}{\partial Y_{i}} &=& \sum_{j}\frac{\partial D(p\| q)}{\partial d_{ij}}\frac{\partial d_{ij}}{\partial Y_{i}}\\ &=& 2\sum_{j}\frac{\partial D(p\| q)}{\partial d_{ij}}(Y_{i}-Y_{j}) \end{eqnarray*} Kullback-Leibler divergence \begin{eqnarray*} D(p\| q) &=& \sum_{k\neq l}p_{kl}\log p_{kl} - p_{kl}\log q_{kl} \end{eqnarray*} \begin{eqnarray*} \frac{\partial D(p\| q)}{\partial d_{ij}} &=& -\frac{\partial \sum_{k\neq l}p_{kl}\log q_{kl}}{\partial d_{ij}}\\ &=& -\sum_{k\neq l}p_{kl}\frac{\partial \log q_{kl}}{\partial q_{kl}}\frac{\partial q_{kl}}{\partial d_{ij}}\\ &=& -\sum_{k\neq l}p_{kl}\frac{1}{q_{kl}}\frac{\partial q_{kl}}{\partial d_{ij}} \end{eqnarray*} $q_{kl}=\frac{(1+d_{kl})^{-1}}{\sum_{m\neq n}(1+d_{mn})^{-1}}$ \begin{eqnarray*} \frac{\partial q_{ij}}{\partial d_{ij}} &=& \frac{-(1+d_{ij})^{-2}}{\sum_{k\neq l}(1+d_{kl})^{-1}}+\frac{2(1+d_{ij})^{-3}}{(\sum_{k\neq l}(1+d_{kl})^{-1})^2}\\ &=& (1+d_{ij})^{-1}(-q_{ij}+2q_{ij}^2)\\ \frac{\partial q_{kl}}{\partial d_{ij}} &=& \frac{2(1+d_{kl})^{-1}(1+d_{ij})^{-2}}{(\sum_{m\neq n}(1+d_{mn})^{-1})^2}\\ &=& 2(1+d_{ij})^{-1}q_{ij}q_{kl}\\ \end{eqnarray*} \begin{eqnarray*} \sum_{k\neq l}p_{kl}\frac{1}{q_{kl}}\frac{\partial q_{kl}}{\partial d_{ij}} &=& -2p_{ij}\frac{1}{q_{ij}}(1+d_{ij})^{-1}q_{ij} + 2\sum_{k\neq l}p_{kl}\frac{1}{q_{kl}}(1+d_{ij})^{-1}q_{kl}q_{ij}\\ &=& -2p_{ij}(1+d_{ij})^{-1} + 2\sum_{k\neq l}p_{kl}(1+d_{ij})^{-1}q_{ij}\\ &=& -2p_{ij}(1+d_{ij})^{-1} + 2q_{ij}(1+d_{ij})^{-1}\\ \end{eqnarray*}
